org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin
Class AeQueuedReceiveDetail

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin.AeQueuedReceiveDetail
public class AeQueuedReceiveDetail
extends java.lang.Object

Light weight JavaBean impl of the queued receive object. Omits the receive data and message receiver in favor of the receiver's xpath location.
